				<p>* note that all the numbers of "- (m/b)illion people in the world would understand Ido" are only <i>hypothetic</i> (and done through math), there is of course no concrete numbers, but in theory!<br>Note the following table of words compared between all 6 languages:</p>
				<p>------------------------</p>
				<p>(The words in parentheses "()" is words that come from the same source, but have gotten a slightly different meaning.)<br>The list goes on... do you need more proof? ;-) Here is the first article of Human Rights:</p>
				<table width="100%" class="ui orange definition table">
